  description: 'In March 1922, six people were bludgeoned to death on a remote Bavarian farmstead. Someone stayed for days afterward — feeding the livestock, lighting fires, eating from the kitchen. Over a century later, nobody knows who killed the Gruber family or why. This is the story of Germany\'s most infamous unsolved crime.',
